data.description: Stunning Gwinnett County ranch home nestled in the top rated Mill Creek High School Cluster! The large rocking chair front porch invites you into the open concept floor plan that is showcased with tons of natural light! The gourmet chef's kitchen is centered around the large granite island with direct sightlines into the huge family room. Every aspect of the primary bedroom is oversized from the actual bedroom, the ensuite bath, and walk-through closet that has direct access to the laundry room! The perfect-sized backyard features a screened-in porch and wrap-around deck with accessibility directly from the driveway. Conveniently located central to schools, parks, and more, don't miss your chance to make this one your own!
